# LawyerConnect

A modern platform connecting clients and lawyers for legal services, built with React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, and Supabase.

🌐 **Live Demo:** [https://law-yer-connect.vercel.app/](https://law-yer-connect.vercel.app/)

---

## Features

- 🔒 User authentication (email/password & Google, powered by Supabase)
- 👩‍⚖️ Lawyer and client account types
- 💬 Real-time chat (Supabase)
- 📊 Analytics dashboard
- 📱 Responsive design (Tailwind CSS)
- ⚡ Fast, serverless deployment (Vercel)

---

## Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/LawYerConnect.git
cd LawYerConnect
```

### 2. Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 3. Set up environment variables

Create a `.env` file in the root directory and add:

```env
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key
```

### 4. Run locally

```bash
npm run dev
```

---

## Deployment

This project is deployed on [Vercel](https://vercel.com/).  
To deploy your own version:

1. Push your code to GitHub.
2. Import your repo on [vercel.com](https://vercel.com/).
3. Add your environment variables in the Vercel dashboard.
4. Deploy!

---

